<div style="margin-left: 2em;"><a href="#toc3">Containment-centric Documentation</a></div>
<div style="margin-left: 1em;"><a href="#toc4">Standard Containment Procedures</a></div>
<div style="margin-left: 2em;"><a href="#toc5">General Facility Security</a></div>
<div style="margin-left: 2em;"><a href="#toc6">On-Site Containment</a></div>
<div style="margin-left: 2em;"><a href="#toc7">Standard Secure Lockers</a></div>
<div style="margin-left: 2em;"><a href="#toc8">Standard Humanoid Containment Cells</a></div>
<div style="margin-left: 1em;"><a href="#toc9">Tips</a></div>
</div>
